platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Join a live class from home

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With Peloton, working out doesn’t have to happen in a silo. Whether you’re into cycling, running, rowing, or yoga, each on-demand workout class is a community affair with a leaderboard full of others cheering you on as well as themed challenges open to all. Plus, it’s easy to stay motivated thanks to the app’s encouraging coaches, and detailed stats help you stay consistent in maintaining your streak.
